title: World English Bible: Old Testament
creator: World English Bible
description: LibriVox recording of The Old Testament of The New English Bible, read by LibriVox volunteers. The World English Bible is a translation of the Bible into modern English. Work on the project began in 1997, but the translation has been released directly into the public domain, free of copyright. It is largely an update of the American Standard Version of 1901, and is intended to be both readable and non-denominational. (Summary by Leon Mire) A LibriVox recording of the World English Bible New Testament is available Here For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org M4B format available

reviews.reviewbody: I've been searching the internet for a free mp3 audio bible for several years. The only other OT I found is full of skips. Thank you so much for this audio bible!
reviews.reviewtitle: Thank you! Thank you! Thank you!
